協同發展<br />\n- 興建東鐵、西鐵快速線並完善輕鐵和西鐵聯乘關係<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V1VCzpw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV1VCzpw.jpg&h=7b29ce56&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RYt8F4w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRYt8F4w.jpg&h=eecde813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>醫療、教育方向</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B2D8F34.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB2D8F34.png&h=cb82275f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"},{"pid":"a71e9b36833998a9b00d3ed3391beb5f9eee676e","tid":1667552,"uid":268123,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T14:16:00.000Z","msg":"根著喺大家嘅稅裏面賠"},{"pid":"12d285f557407d05e8f1b0f59484496d24ac0206","tid":1667552,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T15:10:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"479156146d129b422bb473babad6b81fb482a4ad","tid":1667552,"uid":172826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T15:12:22.000Z","msg":"大家入黎幫手推po 唔好俾手足死得不明不白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【海怡女浮屍最新整合】黃健茵疑似被自殺案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1667382\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1667382</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cc3a0ef5adbfdf4f64f57551cdfdff4d5f13ba48","tid":1667552,"uid":28244,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T15:14:03.000Z","msg":"爆玻璃唔貴 但係d煙同d有害物質入哂車 慢性自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />賣得"},{"pid":"5d0ab022ba5e6951423ea913be654ccdabb672cd","tid":1667552,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T15:18:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h93TUgu.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?